         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>The <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">Mars ʾamin</t:foreign> is a treatise dealing with monophysite doctrine. 
            It is transmitted in the codex unicus <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet119">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien 119</t:ref>
            together with <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1386Fekkar">Fǝkkāre
                                                  malakot</t:ref>, <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1578hamara">Ḥamara nafs</t:ref> and <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2635Dawana">Ḍawana nafs</t:ref>. 
         </t:p>
         </t:abstract>
